      <title>特朗普胜选推动房地美和房利美的僵尸优先股飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/trump-win-supercharges-freddie-mac-fannie-mae-preferred-zombies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场猜测唐纳德·特朗普将解除住房金融机构在危机时期的托管，房利美和房地美发行的长期低迷的优先股股价周三飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/trump-win-supercharges-freddie-mac-fannie-mae-preferred-zombies</guid>
